485
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:55,040
<i>Let's keep the speed up a bit.</i>

486
00:28:55,540 --> 00:28:56,980
[exciting music plays]

487
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:01,180
[Loos] <i>So let's push, mate.</i>

488
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:02,820
[exciting music continues]

489
00:29:04,980 --> 00:29:06,880
{\an8}[Gasly] Where are we
at the moment? Position?

490
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:07,760
{\an8}[Loos] <i>P5.</i>

