547
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:54,100
{\an8}[commentator 1] <i>And we're racing
on the streets of Monaco!</i>

548
00:32:57,920 --> 00:33:00,820
[commentator 2] <i>Aggressive defending
from Ocon on the inside!</i>

549
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,740
[Peckett] <i>This start so far
has been very good.</i>

550
00:33:04,780 --> 00:33:06,680
<i>Sainz the car behind.</i>

551
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,200
[tense music plays]

552
00:33:12,540 --> 00:33:14,620
{\an8}[Peckett] <i>Gap to Sainz 1.2 seconds.</i>

553
00:33:14,660 --> 00:33:16,900
[tense music continues]

554
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,240
{\an8}[Ocon] Yeah, I got hit.

555
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:29,440
{\an8}It's crazy. I had nowhere to go there.

556
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:31,640
Tires feel very fragile at the moment.

557
00:33:33,180 --> 00:33:34,020
[Peckett] <i>Box, box.</i>

558
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:35,380
[Loos] <i>Esteban in.</i>

559
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:40,640
[commentator 3] <i>Ocon now pits
from third place.</i>

560
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:45,820
[tense music continues]

561
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:52,700
{\an8}[commentator 1] <i>Gasly goes through
past his Alpine teammate,</i>

562
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:54,300
<i>goes up into third!</i>

563
00:33:54,840 --> 00:33:58,200
<i>Esteban Ocon down
in fifth place at the moment.</i>

564
00:33:58,240 --> 00:34:00,180
{\an8}[Peckett] <i>Okay, we need
to push now, Esteban.</i>

565
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:09,740
{\an8}[commentator 1] <i>Pierre Gasly
is absolutely charging.</i>

566
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,160
{\an8}[Loos] <i>Pierre, P3.</i>

567
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:18,320
{\an8}<i>Keep your nose clean, stay focused,
and there's some good points here.</i>

568
00:34:25,100 --> 00:34:27,700
{\an8}<i>Possible rain about 16 laps from now.</i>

569
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,400
-[Gasly] I wanna go long.
-[Loos] <i>Copy.</i>

570
00:34:34,700 --> 00:34:35,640
<i>Box, box.</i>

571
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:37,960
[Gasly] So give me rain tires.

572
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:44,340
[commentator 2] <i>It looks like Alpine
are not giving Gasly wet-weather tires.</i>

573
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:46,100
<i>They're giving him dry tires.</i>

574
00:34:46,140 --> 00:34:48,860
<i>That's a real surprise
given there is forecast for rain.</i>

575
00:34:51,240 --> 00:34:52,340
[Gasly] I don't get it.

576
00:34:53,740 --> 00:34:56,080
[Loos] <i>Copy that.
Really not much rain on the radar.</i>

577
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,440
[Gasly] It better not increase.

578
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:01,660
[tense music plays]

579
00:35:07,860 --> 00:35:11,360
{\an8}[Loos] <i>Some reports
of very light rain at turn three.</i>

580
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:15,260
[Gasly] Yeah, I know. That's why I don't
understand why we put on dry tires.

581
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:25,020
{\an8}[Gasly] It's raining a lot now.
Turn eight, there is water.

582
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:26,220
{\an8}For fuck's sake.

583
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:28,880
[dramatic music plays]

584
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:34,520
[commentator 3] <i>Look at the spray.
Absolutely treacherous.</i>

585
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:38,160
{\an8}[Ocon] Raining heavy now. I need to box.

586
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:41,680
{\an8}[Peckett] <i>Okay, Esteban.
Let's box for inters.</i>

587
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,680
[Ocon] Okay, good.

588
00:35:48,780 --> 00:35:50,020
{\an8}I need rain tires.

589
00:35:51,140 --> 00:35:51,980
{\an8}[Loos] <i>Box, box.</i>

590
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:54,280
[commentator 2] <i>Another pit stop
for Gasly.</i>

591
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:56,760
<i>This could have a massive impact
on his race.</i>

592
00:35:57,260 --> 00:36:00,360
{\an8}<i>Oh, if only he was given
the right tires earlier.</i>

593
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:02,580
{\an8}[Loos] <i>So currently, you're P7.</i>

594
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:09,100
{\an8}[Peckett] <i>Esteban, you've got this
under control. Keep it up.</i>

595
00:36:09,140 --> 00:36:10,280
{\an8}Okay.

596
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:12,320
[dramatic music plays]

597
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:17,460
[music fades]

598
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:21,240
{\an8}[commentator 3] <i>Esteban Ocon
comes home to take third place.</i>

599
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:24,880
[Ocon] Yes, guys! Yes!

600
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:25,940
{\an8}[laughs]

601
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:28,460
-[Peckett] <i>Well done.</i>
-[Ocon] Oh my God!

602
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:31,660
[laughs] Woo! Yes!

603
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:39,920
{\an8}[Loos] <i>That's the checkered flag and P7.</i>

604
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:42,940
[Gasly] What the fuck was that?

605
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:47,080
[Gasly] That decision to not give me
the right tires for the rain

606
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:48,320
{\an8}was a mistake.

607
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,800
It cost me the third place.

608
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:53,900
Pretty painful, because this would've been
my first podium with Alpine.

609
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:58,200
You know, as a team,
we still got one car on the podium.

610
00:36:59,120 --> 00:37:00,420
But on my side,

611
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:02,360
I just felt like we gave it away,

612
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,960
and I just felt,

613
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,760
yeah, very... bitter.

614
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:19,620
I want a shower, so I'm gonna leave.

