00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:38,020
that I'm the best driver in the team.

638
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:45,060
{\an8}Let's get on with it.

639
00:38:45,100 --> 00:38:47,520
{\an8}-My contract is up for renewal.
-[man] Lewis, please come back.

